msgid "Automatically Mark Pingbacks/Trackbacks as Spam"
msgstr "Pingback/Trackback automatisch als Spam markieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:186
msgid ""
"Automatically mark pingbacks and trackbacks as spam without OpenAI check"
msgstr ""
"Pingbacks und Trackbacks automatisch als Spam markieren, ohne OpenAI-Prüfung"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:193
msgid "Mark Different Language as Spam"
msgstr "Andere Sprache als Spam markieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:199
msgid ""
"Automatically mark submissions as spam if they are in a different language "
"than your website (useful for single-language websites)"
msgstr ""
"Markieren Sie Beiträge automatisch als Spam, wenn sie in einer anderen "
"Sprache als Ihre Website verfasst sind (nützlich für einsprachige Websites)."

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:205
msgid "Language Mismatch Score Boost"
msgstr "Sprachinkongruenz-Score-Boost"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:214
msgid ""
"Amount to increase spam score when language doesn't match (0.1 - 1.0). "
"Default: 0.3"
msgstr ""
"Betrag zur Erhöhung der Spam-Bewertung, wenn die Sprache nicht übereinstimmt "
"(0,1 – 1,0). Standardwert: 0,3"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:221
msgid "OpenAI Integration"
msgstr "OpenAI-Integration"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:228
msgid "Enable OpenAI Detection"
msgstr "OpenAI-Erkennung aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:234
msgid "Use OpenAI to detect spam"
msgstr "Verwenden Sie OpenAI, um Spam zu erkennen."

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:240
msgid "OpenAI API Key"
msgstr "OpenAI API-Schlüssel"

#. translators: %s: OpenAI API URL
#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:249
msgid ""
"Get your API key from <a href=\"%s\" target=\"_blank\">OpenAI Platform</a>"
msgstr ""
"API-Schlüssel von <a href=\"%s\" target=\"_blank\">der OpenAI-Plattform</a> "
"holen."

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:257
msgid "OpenAI Model"
msgstr "OpenAI-Modell"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:271
msgid "Which AI model to use for spam detection"
msgstr "Welches KI-Modell soll für die Spam-Erkennung verwendet werden?"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:277
msgid "AI Spam Threshold"
msgstr "KI-Spam-Schwellenwert"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:286
msgid ""
"Spam score threshold (0.0 - 1.0). Higher values mean fewer submissions are "
"flagged as spam (less strict). Lower values mean more submissions are "
"flagged as spam (more strict). Default: 0.7"
msgstr ""
"Spam-Score-Schwellenwert (0,0 – 1,0). Höhere Werte bedeuten, dass weniger "
"Beiträge als Spam markiert werden (weniger streng). Niedrigere Werte "
"bedeuten, dass mehr Beiträge als Spam markiert werden (strenger). "
"Standardwert: 0,7"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:293, includes/admin/class-settings.php:637
msgid "Heuristic Detection"
msgstr "Heuristische Erkennung"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:300
msgid "Enable Heuristic Detection"
msgstr "Heuristische Erkennung aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:306
msgid "Use local heuristics to detect spam patterns (works without OpenAI)"
msgstr ""
"Verwenden Sie lokale Heuristiken, um Spam-Muster zu erkennen (funktioniert "
"ohne OpenAI)."

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:312
msgid "Heuristic Spam Threshold"
msgstr "Heuristik-Spam-Schwellenwert"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:321
msgid "Spam score threshold for heuristic detection (0.0 - 1.0). Default: 0.6"
msgstr ""
"Spam-Score-Schwellenwert für heuristische Erkennung (0,0 – 1,0). Höher = "
"strenger. Standardwert: 0,7"

