#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:415, includes/admin/class-settings.php:649
msgid "Maintenance"
msgstr "Wartung"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:422
msgid "Log Retention"
msgstr "Dauer der Protokollspeicherung"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:431
msgid "Days to keep logs (default: 30)"
msgstr "Tage, an denen Protokolle aufbewahrt werden (Standard: 30)"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:437
msgid "Keep Data on Uninstall"
msgstr "Daten bei Deinstallation behalten"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:443
msgid ""
"If enabled, all plugin data (options, submissions, statistics) will be kept "
"when the plugin is deleted. If disabled, all data will be permanently "
"deleted."
msgstr ""
"Wenn diese Option aktiviert ist, bleiben alle Plugin-Daten (Optionen, "
"Übermittlungen, Statistiken) beim Löschen des Plugins erhalten. Wenn diese "
"Option deaktiviert ist, werden alle Daten dauerhaft gelöscht."

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:449
msgid "Enable GitHub Updates"
msgstr "Updates via Github aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:455
msgid ""
"Enable automatic updates from GitHub releases. <strong>Activate at your own "
